Create your bot using @BotFather - give name and get token.
Install packet:
```
yum install epel-release
yum install python34-devel.x86_64
```

3. Create a directory for virtual enviroment (one script - one enviroment):
```
mkdir -p /usr/local/sbin/venvs && cd "$_"
```

4. Create a virtual "home" for bot:
```
pyvenv-3.4 telebot
```

5. Activ virtual enviroment:
```
source bin/activate
```
P.S. You should see "(telebot) root /usr/local/sbin/venvs/telebot #"

6. Check updates and install modul for common with API Telegram:
```
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install pytelegrambotapi
```

7. Check:
```
python
```
P.S. You should see this:
```
Python 3.4.5 (default, May 29 2017, 15:17:55)
[GCC 4.8.5 20150623 (Red Hat 4.8.5-11)] on linux
Type "help", "copyright", "credits" or "license" for more information.
>>>
```

8. Import module:
```
>>> import pytelegrambotapi
```
or
```
>>> import telebot
```

9. Create script:
```
mkdir body && vim body/bot.py
```
```
#!/usr/bin/python3
 
import os
import telebot
import logging
 
TOKEN = os.environ['TELETOKEN']
 
bot = telebot.TeleBot(TOKEN)
logger = telebot.logger
telebot.logger.setLevel(logging.DEBUG)
 
@bot.message_handler(commands=['help', 'start'])
def send_welcome(message):
    bot.reply_to(message, """\
    Hi there, I am EchoBot.\
    I am here to echo your kind words back to you.\
    Just say anything nice and I'll say the exact same thing to you!\
    """)
 
@bot.message_handler(content_types=["text"])
def repeat_all_messages(message):
    bot.send_message(message.chat.id, message.text)
 
bot.polling(none_stop=True)

Start bot for checking:
python3 body/bot.py
And check performance in Telegram!
Create file /etc/systemd/system/venv-telebot.service:

[Unit]
Description=Telegram bot written on python 3.4 and executed at python virtual env
After=syslog.target network.target
 
[Service]
Type=simple
User=nobody
Group=nobody
WorkingDirectory=/usr/local/sbin/venvs/telebot
ExecStart=/usr/local/sbin/venvs/telebot/bin/python3 body/bot.py
Restart=on-abort
 
Environment=VIRTUAL_ENV=/usr/local/sbin/venvs/telebot
Environment=TELETOKEN=AAAAA-hsnheHG3nBSbv2MM23bsallOpwkes
Environment=PATH=$VIRTUAL_ENV/bin:$PATH
 
[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

10. Autoload:
```
systemctl enable venv-telebot.service
```

11. Start bot:
```
systemctl start venv-telebot.service
```
